"Write one JSON object per replayed record to ``PATH`` (``{qualname, "
"latency_ms, failed}``) for post-hoc analysis."
msgstr ""
"将每个重放记录写入一个 JSON 对象到 ``PATH`` (``{qualname, latency_ms, "
